long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: We are providing curated accessibility to the Multilinguals Forward website and networking account links for ease of navigation for Multilinguals Forward's clients. These clients are students with limited or interrupted formal education (who have limited technological literacy and would greatly benefit from this extension), teachers, administrators, and other education policy makers. By having all of Multilinguals Forward's materials in one place, we hope to create a more seamless experience for our users.
